concept.title: Menu Tree

othermeta.name: shortdesc
othermeta.content: Provides an overview of the menu structure in the system display, showing available functions depending on access level and user permissions.

othermeta.name: entities
othermeta.content: menu tree; display interface; navigation panel; event log; measurements module; alarm menu

othermeta.name: tags
othermeta.content: menu navigation, display interface, event log, alarm menu, measurements, ui structure

othermeta.name: usecase
othermeta.content: describe the hierarchical menu structure and navigation options in the system display

conbody.p: The visible content depends on the access level of the logged in user. The menu tree shows the content for a user with the Service access level in the Display.
conbody.note: Fields that are grayed out cannot be changed by the logged in user.
